Hi Magnus! :wave: If you're trying to align a Tag with a single line of Text, you can use the Flex component like below:

```&lt;Flex gap='extra-small'&gt;
  &lt;Tag&gt;In Review&lt;/Tag&gt;
  &lt;Text format={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}&gt;Some text over here&lt;/Text&gt;
&lt;/Flex&gt;```
Thanks for your feedback!
